{
  "stem": "18575.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he found out where this machine is made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was made in the La Hague then The Hague, Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He met the manufacturer, told him the problems, and the manufacturer assured them that the machine would do it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If not, he would make it do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He purchased the machine, shipped it to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The machine did not work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he called the manufacturer, and the manufacturer came in, made-- he was brilliant, the Dutch manufacturer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He made the machine, converted it, and it did perform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he did the repairs in our machine shop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had-- in our refrigeration business, we had a machine shop, so the conversion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then, by word of mouth, this flour salesman told other bakers about the molder former that forms the bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they kept calling and saying, hey, we'd like to buy it one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where do we get it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So Herbie and I, being good friends, I say, why don't we start a company?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we import and we have fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're both single.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We travel to Europe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you got your bakeries, we have our refrigeration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we started that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a rather short time with him-- two, three years-- we started manufacturing a different design machinery for all production, not for bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Became the only and biggest manufacturer of bake-- automatic bakery machinery and ovens in the United States for European-type breads, not for white breads or hot dogs or hamburgers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was called Adamatic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a ego complex of mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1989, a company Hobart, who was international food producing, machinery producer, came to us, started romancing us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to buy us.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
